Add full backend implementation, README, and overlay system

- backend/: FastAPI app with weather, forecast, AQI, location, community, overlay, and upload routes
- AI summaries via OpenAI/DeepSeek with rule-based fallbacks; ECMWF GRIB + OWM dual-source fetching
- server/index.cjs: Express upload server for community photos
- frontend/public/overlays/: manifest + Apple Glass theme tokens for 72 weather GIF overlays
- download_overlays.py: one-time Giphy GIF downloader
- README.md: setup guide, API reference, overlay docs, future updates list
- .gitignore: now excludes venv/, __pycache__/, .env, node_modules/, GRIB data

